        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 0,
            "config": {
              "title": "🌿 You search the grass and...",
              "content": "> The grass stretches endlessly across the valley—lush, waist-high, and swaying with every gust of wind. There’s no way a single pair of eyes could cover it all. Fortunately, you and your companions know how to fan out like professionals.\n\nMinutes pass. The sun presses overhead. The chirping of insects is all you hear.\n\nThen—you stumble.\n\nYour foot catches on something beneath the green. Not a root, but stone. You brush aside a thick cluster of blades, revealing a rough, uneven patch of ground. Nestled between two half-buried rocks, you find it:\n\nA hole.\n\nBarely wider than your shoulders. Jagged at the edges. And dark. So, so dark.\n\nA faint, cool breeze flows from within. No sound. No light. Just the yawning promise of something vast waiting beneath.",
