          "G1": {
            "channelId": "1431901236084473968",
            "baseContent": {
              "title": "🏔️ G1 | Duscur Foothills",
              "description": "> The air grows thin and wild as you reach the northernmost edge of the monastery’s lands. Here lie the Duscur Foothills, cloaked in perpetual shadow beneath the looming silhouettes of mountains that stretch beyond the horizon. Sparse trees cling to life amid the jagged rock and shale, their roots twisting through the cracks like fingers grasping at memory.\n\nA chill mist rolls down from the peaks, curling low around your boots. Somewhere in the distance, the cry of a hawk echoes sharply through the silence, followed by the rumble of unseen stone shifting—was it just a landslide, or something more deliberate?\n\nShattered cairns and half-buried remnants of old campsites dot the trail, vestiges of scouts and exiles who dared tread too far into the borderlands of Duscur. A broken spear is planted in the earth beside a weathered creststone shard, its meaning lost to time.\nSomewhere near, a small cave mouth gapes in the hillside. A flicker of movement—then stillness. Are you being watched?",
