            "baseContent": {
              "title": "🐟 B4 | Fishing Pond And Dining Hall 🍽️",
              "description": "Nestled beside the greenhouse and quietly humming with the scent of wet stone and algae, the pond's surface glimmers with the occasional ripple. Nearby, a weathered stone ledge offers a perch for weary students or eager anglers. Looking over the water deep in thought is Ashe.\n\n---------------------------------------------\n\nAcross from the Fishing Pond is the Dining Hall. Students are spready across various tables enjoying the meal of the day and sharing stories. The Head Chef stands near the food, talking to students about cooking tips. At one of the tables, Ingrid is sitting with Caspar enjoying a quick lunch.",
