            "baseContent": {
              "title": "⚓ G7 | Seaward Expanse",
              "description": "> As you reach the southeasternmost edge of Garreg Mach's borders, the world opens wide into the Seaward Expanse—a lonely, windswept promontory where the land surrenders to the infinite shimmer of the ocean. Briny mist clings to the air, and gulls cry overhead as rolling waves batter the jagged rocks below. Sunlight glints off the water’s surface like diamonds. \n\nA stone outcropping juts into the sea, cracked and half-submerged.\n\nYou spot a weathered bottle caught between two tide-slick rocks.",
