            "type": "display_text",
            "order": 0,
            "config": {
              "title": "Enter The Great Deku Tree",
              "content": "> As you step into the cavernous maw of the Great Deku Tree, the scent of moss and ancient wood envelops you. The dim light filters through the leaves above, casting a verdant glow on everything within. You can hear the distant drip of water, a natural melody that speaks of the tree’s age-old wisdom.\n\nThe first room is vast, with an enormous spider web covering the floor. It's strong enough to stand on, but the webs are woven tightly enough together that it is impossible to fall through. Wouldn't want to come face to face with whatever made that... \n\nAs you step closer into the center of the room, some deku babas emerge from the ground, lunging toward you with their serrated jaws. Luckily you're far enough that they can't reach you, though if you want, you can take them on individually (**?h8-battle-bigbaba**).\n\nYou gaze upward at the tree's ancient interior. Platforms of various heights are scattered throughout, with vast spiderwebs connecting the platforms. The interior of the tree is adorned with thick, tough looking vines which stretch upwards towards the light..",
              "image": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1205174228555403284/1214929279872147546/image.png?ex=69c68790&is=69c53610&hm=acc6c9f0976739e44abc4bb252e769a414df397e8f6d6e133981e655af88a909&",
